These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis
2 different games are played: bridge, monopoly
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, accountant
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, trance
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, alhambra
1. the freelancer is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
5. the freelancer is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
6. the havana-smoker is not to the left of the fan of trance##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Flower      | amaryllis      | bellflower |
| Game          | monopoly      | bridge       |
| Job         | accountant | freelancer  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | satire      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | trance      |
| Cigar         | alhambra    | havana       |

