.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, cycling
House: gothic-revival, art-deco
City: new-york, boston
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, spanish
2 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
2. the person traveling to boston is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the spanish##8
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Sport          | volleyball | cycling |
| House         | gothic-revival  | art-deco  |
| City           | new-york      | boston  |
| Nationality   | spanish     | mexican      |
| Pet           | ferret     | mouse    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship     |

