3. the person who growsbegonia is not to the right of the person who likes chestnut##8
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
5. the social-worker is on the right of the person eating mango##1
6. the person eating mango is not to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##8

